description:
# What can you do with this API?
The Outbound Dialing (OBD) API enables you to connect your customer to the agent efficiently. OBD uses HTTP Basic Authentication. You do not need to disclose your username or password to access the OBD API. Through your account dashboard you can generate unlimited secure API keys to access the OBD API, which also means that you will be restricted to only accessing the data enabled on your OBD user profile.

# Base URL for Integration
> https://obd.kaleyra.com/api/v1/
title: Outbound Dialing (OBD) API
